{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"14":"The Chapters on Gifts"},"section_detail":{"14":{"hadithnumber_first":2375,"hadithnumber_last":2389,"arabicnumber_first":2375,"arabicnumber_last":2389}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":2379,"arabicnumber":2379,"text":"Rapporté par Abu Hurairah : Le Messager d’Allah (ﷺ) a dit : « Il n’y a pas de don à vie. Celui à qui on donne quelque chose comme don à vie, cela lui appartient. »","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Hasan Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Hasan Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Hasan"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Isnaad Hasan"}],"reference":{"book":14,"hadith":5}}]}